@startuml Fabio_Investment_Flows_Component_Interaction
!theme spacelab
title Fabio's Investment Flows - Component Interaction & Data Flow

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

actor User as U
participant "View Controller" as VC
participant "Presenter" as P
participant "Interactor" as I
participant "Service" as S
participant "Backend API" as API
participant "StringToken System" as STS
participant "Metadata Processor" as MP
participant "Coordinator" as C

== User Interaction Flow ==

U -> VC: User taps investment option
activate VC

VC -> I: loadOffer()
activate I

I -> S: getOffer(productId, offerId)
activate S

S -> API: HTTP GET /products/{id}/offers/{offerId}
activate API

API --> S: PurchaseProductModel with StringTokens
deactivate API

S --> I: Response with metadata
deactivate S

I -> STS: Process StringTokens
activate STS

STS -> MP: Parse metadata structure
activate MP

MP --> STS: Processed content fields
deactivate MP

STS --> I: StringWithTypograph objects
deactivate STS

I -> P: present(model: PurchaseProductModel)
activate P

P -> P: createDTO() - Transform to presentation model
P -> P: generateSections() - Create dynamic sections
P -> P: generateDocument() - Process documents

P --> VC: display(dto: PurchaseDetailDTO)
deactivate P

VC -> VC: Update UI with dynamic content
deactivate I

VC --> U: Display investment details
deactivate VC

== Navigation Flow ==

U -> VC: User taps "Invest" button
activate VC

VC -> I: didTapInvest()
activate I

I -> P: presentInputValueScreen(model)
activate P

P -> C: navigateToInputValue()
activate C

C -> C: Create new ViewController with dependencies
C --> VC: Push to InputValue screen
deactivate C
deactivate P
deactivate I
deactivate VC

== Backend Template Processing ==

note over STS, MP
  **Backend Template Architecture:**
  
  1. **StringToken Processing:**
     - Parse value and style from backend
     - Map to PurchaseTypograph enum
     - Create StringWithTypograph objects
  
  2. **Metadata Processing:**
     - Parse complex metadata structures
     - Generate dynamic field mappings
     - Create section-based layouts
  
  3. **Dynamic Content Generation:**
     - Build UI components from metadata
     - Apply backend-controlled styling
     - Support A/B testing variations
end note

== Error Handling Flow ==

U -> VC: User action triggers error
activate VC

VC -> I: performAction()
activate I

I -> S: serviceCall()
activate S

S -> API: API Request
activate API

API --> S: Error Response
deactivate API

S --> I: ApiError
deactivate S

I -> P: presentError(error)
activate P

P -> P: Format error message
P --> VC: displayError(message)
deactivate P

VC -> VC: Show error to user
deactivate I
deactivate VC

== Analytics Flow ==

U -> VC: User interaction
activate VC

VC -> I: userAction()
activate I

I -> I: log(analyticsEvent)
note right: Track user behavior

I -> P: presentData()
activate P

P --> VC: displayContent()
deactivate P

deactivate I
deactivate VC

== Security Flow ==

U -> VC: User attempts sensitive action
activate VC

VC -> I: performSecureAction()
activate I

I -> I: dependencies.auth.authenticate()
note right: PIN validation required

I -> S: secureServiceCall()
activate S

S -> API: Authenticated request
activate API

API --> S: Secure response
deactivate API

S --> I: Success
deactivate S

I -> P: presentSuccess()
activate P

P --> VC: displaySuccess()
deactivate P

deactivate I
deactivate VC

@enduml
